                <mxCell id="p8_et2" value="RUST-ONLY (rust-analyzer enriched)&#10;&#10;typed::Direct&#10;  Direct fn call (fully resolved)&#10;&#10;typed::TraitMethod&#10;  Call through trait object&#10;&#10;typed::DynDispatch&#10;  dyn Trait dispatch&#10;&#10;typed::ClosureInvoke&#10;  Closure call&#10;&#10;dataflow::assign&#10;  Variable assignment flows" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="80" y="550" width="500" height="220" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p8_et3" value="CROSS-LANGUAGE (confidence-scored)&#10;&#10;http_boundary   Rust route ↔ JS/TS fetch&#10;ffi_boundary    Rust extern 'C' ↔ C fn&#10;wasm_boundary   wasm_bindgen ↔ JS import&#10;pyo3_boundary   #[pyfunction] ↔ Python&#10;queue_boundary  producer ↔ consumer&#10;&#10;GRAPH-DERIVED (Datalog/Ascent)&#10;&#10;reachable       Transitive (N hops)&#10;scc_member      Belongs to SCC (cycle)&#10;layer_violation Crosses arch layer rule" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
