                <mxCell id="p8_sm1" value="MCP JOURNEY METRICS&#10;&#10;User configures in &lt; 5 min&#10;Ingest 1000-file repo &lt; 30 sec&#10;Tool response latency &lt; 500ms&#10;Cross-lang boundary &gt;= 0.80 conf&#10;Blast radius 3 hops &lt; 200ms&#10;Token budget: 94%+ reduction&#10;Zero stdout contamination&#10;(logs only to stderr)&#10;&#10;TAURI JOURNEY METRICS&#10;&#10;App cold start &lt; 1 sec&#10;Dashboard &lt; 200ms after ingest&#10;Search results &lt; 150ms keystroke&#10;Blast radius graph &lt; 300ms render&#10;Source panel: always live (G3)&#10;Every UI action shows CLI equiv&#10;Power users → CLI within 7 days" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#aaaaaa;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
