                <mxCell id="p8_conf" value="CONFIDENCE THRESHOLDS (cross-language boundary edges)&#10;&#10;&gt;= 0.80  HIGH    include by default, uncertain=false&#10;0.60-0.79 MEDIUM  include, uncertain=true marker&#10;0.40-0.59 LOW     opt-in only (user must request)&#10;&lt; 0.40   REJECT  not stored&#10;&#10;Signal table (score_boundary_confidence_signal):&#10;RoutePathMatch::Exact +0.40 | HttpMethodMatch +0.20&#10;HandlerNameSimilarity +0.15 | FrameworkBonus +0.10&#10;SameRepoBonus +0.05 | RoutePathMatch::Fuzzy +0.20&#10;MismatchedMethod -0.10" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
